name: EW3.MusicControls
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
For iOS13. Only themes the lockscreen & Prysm controls. Apply with Snowboard with UI extension.

Icons for Prysm music controls also included in .theme folder. Copy all .pngs in the “For Prysm” sub-folder, and paste them by replacing at /Library/Application Support/Prysm/Icons/

Installed to /Library/Themes

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet
